'''Raffaele Bastoni''' (born May 15, 1925) is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[canoe racing|sprint canoer]] who competed in the early 1950s. He finished 17th in the [[Canoeing at the 1952 Summer Olympics - Men's K-2 10000 metres|K-2 10000 m]] event at the [[1952 Summer Olympics]] in [[Helsinki]].

